==Sources== * Batschmann, Oskar & Griener, Pascal. ''Hans Holbein''. Reaktion Books, 1999. {{ISBN|1-86189-040-0}} * Goldberg Jonathan. ''Desiring Women Writing: English Renaissance Examples''. Stanford University Press, 1997. {{ISBN|0-8047-2983-2}}
{{Hans Holbein the Younger}}
